[vc_row css=”.vc_custom_1581597772628{margin-top: 55px !important;}”][vc_column offset=”vc_col-md-6″][vc_column_text css=”.vc_custom_1708433894790{padding-top: 30px !important;}” css_animation=”bottom-to-top”]

ASNU – Classic GDI (Gasoline Direct Injection)

[/vc_column_text]

[vc_column_text css=””]

The ASNU Classic GDI system has been designed for comparing injector against injector at a safe operating level and is suitable for use by apprentice level mechanics to Master level engineers.

To enable a safe and easy examination of the injectors performance, the ASNU system runs the injectors at a lower and safer operating fuel pressure of up to a maximum of 10 bar.

The ASNU Classic GDI injector test machine allows the user to safely examine the injectors Spray pattern in greater detail for any discrepancies in the fuel distribution and atomisation.

[/vc_column_text]

[/vc_column][vc_column offset=”vc_col-md-6″][vc_column_text]
